title: Amiga Paula does XM: Gusse - Escape Velocity (A1200🎧Dolbyfied)
description:

Art "Popup Sweetheart" by Facet/Bonzai^Genesis Projet^Lemon^SWEET16, 2nd at Gerp 2024.

Gusse at Soundcloud:
https://soundcloud.com/gusse_dsx

Made using real A1200 Rev. 1D.4 audio. Playback from DeliTracker 2.34 with 14Bit-NotePlayer 4.30:

- Normal mixing with 44336 Hz mixing frequency

- Module reports 30 channels
